item.obf_query:
t.row_id in (
	select art_exbpic_pic_id
	from art_exb_pic
	where art_exbpic_exb_id=[row_id]
)

t.row_id in (
	select tp_piece_id
	from art_tag_piece
	where tp_tag_id=[row_id]
)
